---
// src/components/Vision.astro
---

<section class="w-full py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-brand-light dark:bg-brand-dark">

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-brand-accent dark:text-white mb-8 leading-tight">
        What We Are Working Toward
      </h2>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
    
    
    <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
      
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We are working toward building a focused and scalable craft initiative. Our objectives include training a small group of artisans each year, setting up a reliable workshop, and developing a production process that ensures quality and consistency. At the same time, we aim to expand our reach through digital platforms, making our products accessible to a global audience.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our mission is to revive the art of Khatam by passing its knowledge to a new generation of makers. We focus on supporting individuals from underserved communities, helping them develop skills that lead to dignity, independence, and creative expression. Through this journey, we aim to protect cultural heritage while building real opportunities for people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:pt-4">
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
        <div class="text-brand-gold font-serif text-xl mb-2">01.</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-white tracking-wide">
          Preserve traditional craft
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
        <div class="text-brand-gold font-serif text-xl mb-2">02.</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-white tracking-wide">
          Train 5 artisans per year
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
        <div class="text-brand-gold font-serif text-xl mb-2">03.</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-white tracking-wide">
          Build sustainable production system
        </h3>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>